title: Down and Dirty with Jim Norton S01E01 2008-10-03
description:
Down and Dirty with Jim Norton on HBO. S01E01 - airdate 10-03-08.  

From the stage of the Bergen Performing Arts Center in New Jersey, Jim Norton - 
along with series deejay Lemmy from Motorhead - welcomes some of the country's 
top comics to perform their most outrageous adults-only routines in front of 
a raucous overflow audience.

Featuring Anthony Jeselnik, Whitney Cummings, Jim Florentine and Artie Lange.
